## TL;DR for Cursor

- Never hand-edit `Formula/*.rb`, `bucket/*.json`, `choco/**/*.nuspec`
- Node 24 LTS + pnpm 10 only
- All GitHub Actions pinned to full commit SHA with tagged comment
- Conventional Commits; release-please handles releases
- Max 300 LOC per source file
- Dark mode + light mode both tested
